name: Quad2Quad
tag_list: college, college-visits, campus, ivies, tours, college-admissions
description: Mobile app for college visits for iphone
overview: ￼ Susan Jones and Elizabeth Van Sant are the co-founders of Quad2Quad, an educational technology company. Quad2Quad is a new college visiting mobile app that is designed to do the hard work of gathering all the necessary data in one place: updates on times for tours and info sessions, handy alerts on interviews and reservations , parking perils and admissions office closures. It will soon include social networking opportunities for high school students as they plan and experience college tours, building their increased involvement and interest in the college visiting process.
